cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with matching patches of a video to a set of reference patches in real-time, and also demonstrates real-time video processing for various applications.
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with video processing and matching.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses an algorithm for matching patches and finding potential matches.
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is possible as the paper deals with searching for nearest neighbors.
5. cs.MM (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper demonstrates various artistic effects that can be applied in real-time video processing.
